"Network partitions should be rare but net gear continues to cause more issues than it should. Networking configuration errors, black holes, dropped packets, and brownouts, remain a popular discussion point in post mortems industry-wide."

James Hamilton, "Stonebraker on CAP Theorem and Databases"
